# Task 3 - IAM Solution Design

## User Lifecycle Management

### Proposed Solution

* Integrate IAM with the HR system.
* Automate onboarding and offboarding.
* Automate role updates when employees change positions.

### Benefits

* Reduced manual work.
* Faster account creation.
* Reduced risk of orphaned accounts.

## Access Control

### Proposed Solution

* Implement RBAC.
* Apply least privilege principles.
* Deploy MFA for all users.
* Conduct periodic access reviews.

### Benefits

* Improved security.
* Better compliance.
* Easier access management.

## Business Alignment

The solution supports TechCorp's security goals, operational efficiency, and digital transformation initiatives.
